title: [Gyldemar Green, Forest]
description: A large maoral tree lies toppled on the ground leaving an opening in the canopy that allows moonlight to filter down, brightening the area.  The root mass of the toppled tree is large, though surprisingly shallow.  The easiest way around the tree appears to be over it.
